1 (..../Day16$ cut -f3 Day16.transcripts.gtf.tmap | sort | uniq -c | grep i -> lalu cek manual berapa nilai i)

###
Apply to question 31-35. 
Perform the differential gene expression analysis. For this, in a first stage run cuffmerge using the provided annotation to merge and reconcile the two sets of cufflinks transcripts. Make a note of the resulting file, ‘merged.gtf’. In a second step, use cufdiff to perform the differential expression analysis.
###

File GTFs.txt:
-----------------
/media/sf_v2/gencommand_proj4/Cufflinks/Day8/transcripts.gtf
/media/sf_v2/gencommand_proj4/Cufflinks/Day16/transcripts.gtf
-----------------

File commands/com.cuffdiff:
----------------- 
WORKDIR=/media/sf_v2/gencommand_proj4
THDIR=/media/sf_v2/gencommand_proj4/Tophat
ANNOT=/media/sf_v2/gencommand_proj4/athal_genes.gtf
mkdir -p $WORKDIR/Cuffmerge $WORKDIR/Cuffdiff
cuffmerge -g $ANNOT -p 2 -o $WORKDIR/Cuffmerge $WORKDIR/commands/GTFs.txt
cuffdiff -o $WORKDIR/Cuffdiff -p 2 $WORKDIR/Cuffmerge/merged.gtf \
$THDIR/Day8/accepted_hits.bam $THDIR/Day16/accepted_hits.bam 
-----------------
sh commands/com.cuffdiff >& com.cuffdiff.log

31. How many genes (loci) were reported in the merged.gtf file?
129 (..../$ cut -f9 merged.gtf | cut -d ‘ ‘ -f2 | sort -u | wc -l)
32. How many transcripts?
207 (..../$ cut -f9 merged.gtf | cut -d ‘ ‘ -f4 | sort -u | wc -l)
33. How many genes total were included in the gene expression report from cuffdiff?
129 (..../$ cut -f1 gene_exp.diff | sort -u | wc -l -> lalu dikurang 1 untuk header)
34. How many genes were detected as differentially expressed?
4 (..../$ grep yes gene_exp.diff | cut -f1 | sort -u | wc -l)
35. How many transcripts were differentially expressed between the two samples?
4 (..../$ grep yes isoform_exp.diff | cut -f1 | sort -u | wc -l)

